{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"Credit scoring is one of the most widely used credit risk analysis tools to rank borrowers by their credit worthiness. Credit scoring is performed using a credit scorecard. Credit scorecards model different characteristics of a customer (age, residential status, etc.), translate them into points and sum the points to compute the credit score. The credit score summarizes the credit worthiness of customers. High credit scores correspond to low-risk customers, and conversely. "}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"In order to assess the predictive ability of a credit scorecard there exists several statistical methodologies, which require the following:"}]},
{"className":"ListParagraph","type":"ordered","children":[
{"className":"ListItem","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"scores associated to each name or observation in the credit scorecard ("},
{"className":"EquationNode","text":"","encoding":"tex","mathmlString":"","displayStyle":false,"texString":"scores"},
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":")"}]},
{"className":"ListItem","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"probability of default corresponding to each score ("},
{"className":"EquationNode","text":"","encoding":"tex","mathmlString":"","displayStyle":false,"texString":"defaultProbs"},
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":")"}]},
{"className":"ListItem","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"indicator variable to signal if an observation is a defaulter or otherwise ("},
{"className":"EquationNode","text":"","encoding":"tex","mathmlString":"","displayStyle":false,"texString":"defaultIndicators"},
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":")"}]}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"In order to better evaluate the capability of model to classify we split the dataset into training and test datasets."}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"cv = cvpartition(sc.Data.(sc.ResponseVar), 'HoldOut') ;"}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"trainingIdx = training(cv) ;"}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"testIdx = test(cv) ;"}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":""}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"Setting up training data","underline":true}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"scores.training = score(sc, sc.Data(trainingIdx,:));"}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"defaultProbs.training = probdefault(sc, sc.Data(trainingIdx,:));"}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"defaultIndicators.training = sc.Data.(sc.ResponseVar)(trainingIdx) ~= sc.GoodLabel;"}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":""}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":"Setting up test data","underline":true}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"scores.test = score(sc, sc.Data(testIdx,:));"}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"defaultProbs.test = probdefault(sc, sc.Data(testIdx,:));"}]},
{"className":"LineNode","children":[
{"className":"PlainTextNode","text":"defaultIndicators.test = sc.Data.(sc.ResponseVar)(testIdx) ~= sc.GoodLabel;"}]},
{"className":"RichTextParagraphNode","align":"left","children":[
{"className":"RichTextNode","text":""}]},
